**/obj/
/TestResults/
*.trx
/node_modules/
/dist/
/build/
/out/
/coverage/
/publish/
/AppPackages/
/BundleArtifacts/
/MsixPackages/

# IDE and OS local state
.vs/
.idea/
**/.godot/
**/.mono/
*.user
*.suo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Codex runtime-local state. Tracked .codex/goals and .codex/state markdown
# remain public project batons; runtime skills/auth/cache/session material does not.
/.codex/*
!/.codex/goals/
!/.codex/goals/**/*.md
!/.codex/state/
!/.codex/state/**/*.md

